      <p>The startup math for a Lewiston dispensary depends on whether you build out a new location or take over an existing commercial space. A typical 1,200-1,500 square foot buildout in Lewiston costs $150,000-$300,000, depending on the condition of the space and the quality of finishes. Mill buildings offer character but may require additional ventilation and security upgrades.</p>
